<font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>次回ONEPIECE</b></font>

324
00:23:22,960 --> 00:23:23,820
<font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>这里是我的台词吧</b></font>

325
00:23:24,290 --> 00:23:25,280
<font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>次回ONEPIECE</b></font>

